      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZENVO YOYO (4) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (31.34) in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Looks the one to beat on her best form. ADHANA LULU (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Murray Bridge behind Our Beaver (31.05) in a Grade 6. Has the pace to be prominent. Can measure up. RAVEN PETER (1) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.5 lengths from the winner State Of Madness in second(31.72) at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Leading player again. ADHANA LAYLA (2) cannot be underestimated.",
